@page "/loggedin"

<div class="container my-4">
    <div class="row">
        <div class="col-md-4 mb-4">
            <div class="card shadow-sm h-100">
                <img src="images/kazir.png" alt="AlienCore ESP Gateway Logo" class="card-img-top" />
                <div class="card-body">
                    <p>
                        In the far reaches of the <strong>Zeta Reticuli</strong> system, a
                        brilliant cybernetic engineer named <em>Ka’Zir Vel‑Tarn</em> emerged
                        from the Stellar Mind Halls—a place where only the most advanced
                        hybrid beings trained in quantum logic and extrasensory synchronization
                        were educated.
                    </p>
                    <p>
                        Gifted with a rare neural augmentation known as the
                        <strong>Neuro‑Spatial Relay Cortex</strong>, Ka’Zir developed the ability
                        to interface with both machine code and higher‑dimensional frequencies
                        simultaneously. This gave him insight into the subtle threads of
                        consciousness traveling across the stars—what humans call ESP.
                    </p>
                    <p>
                        During his time stationed near Earth as part of the Galactic
                        Observational Accord, Ka’Zir witnessed the chaos and inefficiency in
                        human data systems. Yet he saw potential in the fusion of human
                        intuition and Zetan technology. Driven by this vision, he created the
                        <strong>AlienCoreESPGateway</strong>—a bridge between Earth’s
                        signal‑based technologies and cosmic cognitive telemetry.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-8 mb-4">
            <div class="card shadow-sm mb-4">
                <div class="card-header">
                    <h5 class="card-title mb-0">Home</h5>
                </div>
                <div class="card-body">
                    <p class="card-text">This is the home page of the AlienCore ESP Gateway application.</p>
                    <p>Use the navigation menu to explore different features and functionalities.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="card shadow-sm">
                <div class="card-body">
                    <div class="card-header">
                        <h5 class="card-title mb-0">The Origin of AlienCoreESPGateway</h5>
                    </div>
                    <p>
                        In the early 2030s, deep within a classified sector of the Mojave
                        Desert, an enigmatic facility known only as the
                        <strong>AlienCoreESPGateway</strong> emerged—its architecture unlike
                        anything built by human hands. Designed in collaboration between
                        Earth’s brightest engineers and a Zeta Reticulan visionary named
                        <strong>Ka’zir</strong>, the gateway was more than just a tech hub; it
                        was a bridge between civilizations.
                    </p>
                    <p>
                        Ka’zir, a cybernetic diplomat and systems architect from the Zeta star
                        system, arrived on Earth during a covert knowledge exchange program
                        initiated after the First Contact Accords. With advanced knowledge of
                        neural mesh computing and quantum coherence telemetry, Ka’zir sought
                        to solve one of humanity’s greatest challenges: secure, high‑bandwidth,
                        multidimensional data transfer between human‑operated edge devices and
                        the XenoGrid—a galactic information network used by hundreds of species.
                    </p>
                    <p>
                        Together with a coalition of human scientists and AI systems, Ka’zir
                        introduced the concept of the <strong>ESP Gateway</strong>—a hybrid
                        infrastructure combining Earth’s emerging technologies with Zeta
                        cybernetic protocols. The <strong>AlienCoreESPGateway</strong> was born
                        as a multi‑platform telemetry system capable of ingesting
                        quantum‑signed data from field devices (“Scouts”), validating their
                        origin using cosmic entropy signatures, and securely transmitting them
                        through a RabbitMQ‑backed <em>QuantumQueue</em> and into the
                        <em>TimeVaultDB</em>.
                    </p>
                    <p>
                        Today, the facility not only powers interplanetary research missions
                        but also enables secure cosmic communication through its real‑time
                        SignalR hub known as <strong>XenoHub</strong>. Ka’zir, now a respected
                        emissary, continues to evolve the platform—ensuring AlienCoreESPGateway
                        remains the Earth's vanguard into a connected galactic future.
                    </p>
                    <img src="images/aliencoreespgateway.png" alt="AlienCore ESP Gateway Logo" class="img-fluid rounded-end" />
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
